   Le blog de Mathilde

   I'm Mathilde, I've been living in Boston, MA since 2012. Welcome on to
   my blog, where you can find stories about my American road trips and
   how it is to live in Boston as a Frenchie. In the daily life, I'm a
   tourist guide right here in Boston where I founded my own company for
   French tourists. I'm also a travel writer for the Michelin guides, and
   I have published several books for French publishers about yoga,
   meditation, games etc. You can also find me on social media:
     *
     *

